snippet.title: Angel Stone Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
With the official gameplay trailer, take a glimpse into the world of Angel Stone, a post-apocalyptic hardcore hack-and-slash RPG of biblical proportions! 

Head over to www.angelstonegame.com click the 'Pre-Register' tab and fill in your information.
Remember to put a valid email address! Those selected will receive an email containing Angel Stone access.

If you want to explore the world of Angel Stone, sign up now!

Resistance Arise!

- Android download: https://bit.ly/33aGjAg
- iOS download: https://apple.co/3rBpLuB
